messages.message:
Seems like `/usr/local/opt/libnfs/lib/libnfs.11.dylib` is not present when you do `brew install libnfs`

I did see `/usr/local/opt/libnfs/lib/libnfs.13.dylib`
and `/usr/local/opt/libnfs/lib/libnfs.dylib`

so fixed it by `cp /usr/local/opt/libnfs/lib/libnfs.13.dylib /usr/local/opt/libnfs/lib/libnfs.11.dylib`
